![Ep181.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1623276817368-8LEF293PTKL36ORIOUVN/Ep181.jpg)

WHICH WAS WORSE IS BACK! The series that has The Don and Dan The Comic Man defending the indefensible returns with a rare wrinkle. In this episode, the guys pit 2010's Jonah Hex against 1986's Howard The Duck! Thing is, neither Dan nor The Don has seen EITHER film until this moment! What film will be crown definitively worse? You decide as you listen to another banger episode of the Major Issues Podcast!

  
Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
